description: Minimal comments — only non-obvious constraints and domain rules
globs: "**/*.py"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Comments Policy

- Default: no new comments. Prefer clearer names and structure.
- Add comments only for non-obvious constraints, security warnings, domain rules, or tradeoffs.
- Allowed markers: `TODO(<issue>):`, `FIXME(<issue>):`, `NOTE:`, `SECURITY:` — no untracked TODO/FIXME.
- No docstrings that repeat signatures. No decorative section comments.
- Prefer English for new comments; preserve existing Korean comments unless editing them directly.
